# Tokyo Station

This is **Tokyo Station** (東京駅), located in **Tokyo, Japan**.

The distinctive red brick building in the foreground is the historic Tokyo Station building, which was completed in 1914 and designed in a European Renaissance Revival style. It's one of Japan's most iconic railway stations and has been carefully restored to its original appearance. The modern skyscrapers visible in the background are characteristic of Tokyo's contemporary skyline, creating a striking contrast between the historic station and the modern city around it.
